{"tid":878219,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"《一人燒肉機》窩在家享受獨屬於自己的那份美味就是爽","createTime":"2018-10-27T03:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T11:38:56.000Z","uid":1121,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c53852678c62cff024c492924061df718dc84357","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110021_15bae975a8d6b2aa523fc91e19e5217f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110021_15bae975a8d6b2aa523fc91e19e5217f.png&h=fbc7672a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於喜歡〝一個人〞出門的朋友，應該都有過去餐廳用餐覺得憋扭的狀況吧，比方說燒烤店、羊肉爐這種一堆人用餐的場合，提出〝我只有一個人吃飯〞的需求，還真有點OOXX，但我就是想吃燒肉啊怎麼辦？今天喜歡把肉肉跟蔬菜放在烤盤上的朋友有福了，日本的THANKO(サンコー)公司就在這兩天，推出了「一人燒肉機」，不管你今天是要處理肉排、魚肉、漢寶包還是煎顆蛋，這台機器都可以滿足你的需求~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110113_b9d64a925b3badef7c15634ebfc45d67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110113_b9d64a925b3badef7c15634ebfc45d67.png&h=397490cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一人燒肉機(卓上ひとり焼肉プレート)簡單來講就是小型的桌上型燒肉機，原理跟外面店家所使用的東西差不多，但大小只有B5這麼大，不但好拿烤盤什麼的也好清洗或方便收納，而且售價才3480(税込)日幣<br />\n真心覺得好說(拇指)"},{"pid":"6d1d0c0737a18d13284806088d18767ea3a09545","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110156_276c6008bbda0fd156844475f0b0f214.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110156_276c6008bbda0fd156844475f0b0f214.png&h=9ab3598a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來喔！鄉親啊~試想你是那種喜歡偶爾來犒賞自己一下的朋友，想出去吃怕量太多吃不完，那這個一人燒肉機是不是就有夠讚了<br />\n食材自己準備量多量少自己控，吃的爽又不用怕浪費啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110236_58965d470627de246dc1e541ebb80f2b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110236_58965d470627de246dc1e541ebb80f2b.gif&h=2a3fda15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且重點是什麼？雖然阿漆截的是GIF，但那個〝滋滋滋滋滋滋滋滋滋滋〞肉肉在烤盤上發出的聲音，齁~還真的是讓人無法抗拒啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110315_1bc6e1001662bfc322f8affe8ddd8b6a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110315_1bc6e1001662bfc322f8affe8ddd8b6a.gif&h=10448c2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46cba83e2a1f7e378b46d7497db7d38779d6436e","tid":878219,"uid":2949,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n唔能用鐵板隔離班粉膠唔能我攬女鋸和牛~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我條會女詐形的嗎, 比多20皮唔能~~~&quot;JAR JAR 聲&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21894fef767bf2c284107aab23ab6dbc44eaf327","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"接下來冬天要到了，台灣你也知道一到冬天冷氣團下來，就是那種又濕又冷的天氣，出門要撐傘還要弄得一身濕<br />\n那不如在家好好享受美味豈不是很好，又暖又爽~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/110424_4556214114bed27ff44f114606c46f1c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F110424_4556214114bed27ff44f114606c46f1c.gif&h=023f7d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我自己都覺得犯賤幹嘛抓GIF抓成這樣，搞得我現在好餓真的是...<br />\n齁！好想吃燒肉啊＞＜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/48/47/pZuRop_bl6KXrg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F48%2F47%2FpZuRop_bl6KXrg.gif&h=47e64fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fce86c02037cf066dcb73d508ae9d48451816f7","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"這裡有聲音，慎入...別說我沒警告你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YdHo4eihFag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYdHo4eihFag&d=J905N8VzsThzpFTMnrW4iFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=75315ec4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YdHo4eihFag</a>"},{"pid":"07aaba13dcfb0ceda631eceb34b65c1a22ab45b4","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6ec2b447af3ea8d793d475c6ccbae739d79174","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bc18ff8e10411f551add5473311a4342ae804e","tid":878219,"uid":25028,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"買個大d既都可以一個人燒架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fdf93d68a5de756eefb85a5b102e9fe9119423","tid":878219,"uid":150912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n我屋企有電爐同煎pan一樣做到<br />\n之前已經燒過"},{"pid":"6d327628504660388c6a725d4e107fe7f7f5741a","tid":878219,"uid":164751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"如果住宿舍細細地玩下ok嘅"},{"pid":"80c8a1cad3c6a7959675d62082062641e7e1179a","tid":878219,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0092287197e848f49e7eb5e01f419788bdc8882b","tid":878219,"uid":7330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"食完成屋油煙， 諗起都臭"},{"pid":"8778ae240f65367c1ee02157158e9a5cae1d587b","tid":878219,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48bc18ff8e10411f551add5473311a4342ae804e","tid":878219,"uid":25028,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"買個大d既都可以一個人燒架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:29:17.000Z","msg"